    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The children and youth under the teacher&apos;s care differ widely in disposition, habits, and training. Some have no definite purpose or fixed principles. They need to be awakened to their responsibilities and possibilities....",
