    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "He who discerns the opportunities and privileges <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"104\"></span> of his work will allow nothing to stand in the way of earnest endeavor for self-improvement. He will spare no pains to reach the highest standard of excellence. All that he desires his pupils to become, he will himself strive to be.&mdash;<span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"TSS 118.1\" data-link=\"121.489\"><em>Testimonies on Sabbath-School Work</em>, 118, 119</span>.",
